mxCell.value: Make changes on a non-master branch
Create Pull Request to merge with master
Connect local git to github remote
We can use Travis to test and deploy our code
Travis does work based on the .travis.yml file

language: generic
sudo: required
services:
  - docker

before_install:
  - docker build -t wltsankalpa/docker-react-web-app -f Dockerfile.dev .

script:
  - docker run -e CI=true wltsankalpa/docker-react-web-app npm run test

deploy:
  provider: elasticbeanstalk
  region: "us-west-2"
  app: "docker"
  env: "Docker-env"
  bucket_name: "elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-306476627547"
  bucket_path: "docker"
  on:
    branch: master
  access_key_id: $AWS_ACCESS_KEY
  secret_access_key:
    secure: "$AWS_SECRET_KEY"
